com.researchspace.repository.spi

Interface RepositoryConfigurer


  • public interface RepositoryConfigurer
    Returns information about how the deposit can be configured by the client.
    Provides read-only methods which can be used to construct or configure a UI for repository submission.

      • getLicenseConfigInfo

        default LicenseConfigInfo getLicenseConfigInfo()
        Gets configurable list of possible licenses for this repository.
        The default implementation provided by this interface returns an empty list, but allows user-supplied licenses.
        Returns:
        a LicenseConfigInfo
        Since:
        0.1.6

      • getOtherProperties

        default java.util.Map<java.lang.String,RepoProperty> getOtherProperties()
        Gets an optional list of additional repository metadata properties that can be configured by the end-user.
        The default implementation returns an empty map.
        Returns:
        a Map
